    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it shows. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a peek!",
