    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for linear power delivery. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Maintenance is current and comprehensive, including a documented subframe reinforcement, Beisan Systems VANOS refresh, and rod bearing service. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and a factory-spec suspension geometry. The exterior retains its factory-correct finish with zero panel gaps or oxidation, while the interior shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster. This is a mechanically superlative specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
