    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that defines the term 'mint.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain or snow. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks in the paint. The factory alloy wheels are flawless, with no curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, still carrying that new-car scent. The premium leather seats show zero signs of wear or bolster creasing, and the high-tech infotainment system still has the original protective film on the screen. Mechanically, the car is flawless, with a full documented service history from the authorized dealership. Every button, switch, and feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The sale includes all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual set, and the original window sticker. If you are looking for a collector-grade example that requires zero compromises, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
